
actor Customer
participant "Proprietary Channel\n(MyMTN APP&WEB)" as APP
participant MADAPI
participant AirServer
participant CIS

Customer->APP: Clicks on the Subscription History menu to \n view for subscriptions within specific period
APP->MADAPI: Requests customer airtime sales subscription History menu
MADAPI->AirServer: Requests for all airtime sales request within specific period.
MADAPI->CIS: Requests for all data subscription sales within specific period.
AirServer-->MADAPI: Responds with all airtime sales within specified period
CIS-->MADAPI: Responds with all data subscription sales within specified period
MADAPI->MADAPI: Merges all sirtime and data sales to create subscription history response
MADAPI->APP: Responds with subscription History data